    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>请注意：Shrine's Legacy 仅支持单人游戏和本地合作模式</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/bf3005053deaa39332dba9898c832141.avif?t=1766001126\" width=780 height=86 /></span>黑暗正逐渐笼罩阿德米亚大陆。邪恶势力步步紧逼，唯有两位年轻的英雄——里奥与蕾玛——能挺身而出，唤醒“施莱恩之剑”的力量，阻止世界陷入毁灭。在踏上拯救之路之前，他们必须先集齐八颗蕴含魔法的元素宝石，修复施莱恩之剑，并帮助旅途中所遇见的居民。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/78bf260fd071cf43e560e1272bec0748.poster.avif?t=1766001126\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/78bf260fd071cf43e560e1272bec0748.webm?t=1766001126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/78bf260fd071cf43e560e1272bec0748.mp4?t=1766001126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款受超级任天堂经典启发的动作 RPG。你将探索广阔多彩的魔法世界，以实时战斗与装备养成系统迎战强敌。冒险中，你将组成一支双人英雄小队：同伴既可以由 AI 协助，也可以在双人模式中由朋友一同操控。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/e01eedb720a4438ad08ea29c6d04d327.avif?t=1766001126\" width=780 height=111 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿德米亚大地上散布着无数秘密与奇遇。材料、魔法珠宝、祖尔与稀世宝藏都潜藏在未知的角落。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入各式各样的地下城，挑战潜伏其中的怪物与首领；获取宝藏，强化自身实力，获得更强大的魔法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素魔法不仅是战斗的利器，也是解谜的关键。运用智慧与力量，破解机关、穿越障碍，才能继续冒险的步伐。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/28151592f86e59396ea0057e41eeff60.poster.avif?t=1766001126\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/28151592f86e59396ea0057e41eeff60.webm?t=1766001126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/28151592f86e59396ea0057e41eeff60.mp4?t=1766001126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/125c765bfb24a412b1516ab75c4179bf.avif?t=1766001126\" width=780 height=86 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿德米亚正处于毁灭的边缘。没有牺牲，就没有胜利。为了拯救至亲与家园，里奥与蕾玛究竟愿意付出多大代价？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这段由角色与羁绊驱动的史诗旅程中，你将见证友情与牺牲，喜悦与痛苦。当至爱之人离去，他们，又将如何面对？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >施莱恩之剑已在等待，属于英雄的冒险，即将启程! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/b5949bb4843a1d881a9bbf1b170ac0c0.poster.avif?t=1766001126\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/b5949bb4843a1d881a9bbf1b170ac0c0.webm?t=1766001126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435410/extras/b5949bb4843a1d881a9bbf1b170ac0c0.mp4?t=1766001126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*请注意：Shrine's Legacy 仅支持单人游戏和本地合作模式<strong>仅限</strong></i></p>",
